        "subject": "LU-20109 build: remove lustre-client from lustre-dkms.spec.in",
        "message": "LU-20109 build: remove lustre-client from lustre-dkms.spec.in\n\nThe package name of Lustre client modules provided\nby lustre-client-dkms is kmod-lustre-client or\nlustre-client-kmp instead of lustre-client. This\npatch removes lustre-client from lustre-dkms.spec.in.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/65208\nLustre-commit: TBD (from d66e0a620586310b1aa9f97b0b739963cdc2707f)\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: trivial clientextra_install_params=\"--dkms\" \\\n  serverextra_install_params=\"--dkms\"\n\nChange-Id: Ib8d529b016c918c4c83e5688d3c6246a6ef590b3\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\n"
